{"TopicId":163126,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"[HELP!] How do I decode localized strings?","CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T02:42:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T02:42:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been successful thus far in reading ConfigNodes, but now I\u0027ve encountered a new problem.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EPART\n{\n\t...\n\ttitle = #autoLOC_500592 //#autoLOC_500592 = Mk3 Liquid Fuel Fuselage Short\n\t...\n}\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I decode localized strings?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T03:13:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn many UI fields, you can include them directly in-line and the core game code will take care of it for you:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/SmartTankPart.cs#L159\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/SmartTankPart.cs#L159\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/SettingsView.cs#L46\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HebaruSan/SmartTank/blob/master/src/SettingsView.cs#L46\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nOtherwise you can call Localizer.Format (via\u00A0\u0022using KSP.Localization;\u0022) to get the formatted string\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/HebaruSan/Astrogator/blob/master/src/TransferView.cs#L58-L59\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/HebaruSan/Astrogator/blob/master/src/TransferView.cs#L58-L59\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nFull details:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/157804-modders-notes-for-13/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T03:55:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDamn, man 3 for 3 --- you\u0027re good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T05:29:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223117316\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163126\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499745355\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022139010\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xyphos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Xyphos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDamn, man 3 for 3 --- you\u0027re good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re asking questions that I\u0027ve had to investigate myself fairly recently, so it\u0027s my turn\u00A0to pay it forward. Once you get to more difficult stuff, I\u0027ll pipe down and someone else will step in (probably DMagic \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xyphos","CreatedById":139010,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-11T06:05:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223117376\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022163126\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499750955\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HebaruSan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n36 minutes ago, HebaruSan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re asking questions that I\u0027ve had to investigate myself fairly recently, so it\u0027s my turn\u00A0to pay it forward.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFair enough, and much appreciated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-12T16:30:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t need a string replacement you can also use Localizer.GetStringByTag()\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}